snippet.title: Seal: travelers of destiny - gameplay (shikara tower)
snippet.description:
Seal: travelers of destiny is korean RPG for PC, it was also translated to japanese and Chinese.
It was released in 1999 in Korea and in 2000 in Japan and Chinese (i think so)
